  "excerpt": "For some upcoming projects, I got a chance to visit the Varga Store headquarters. I first fell in love with their location in Santa Monica many years ago when walking along Main Street. Now I love their shop in my…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2014/11/fashion-friday-2",
  "legacyFile": "blog__2014__11__fashion-friday-2.html",
  "imageCount": 6,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327582380-75DLRGAVY6YFVYRJ5S37/14a-IMG_1641.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>For some upcoming projects, I got a chance to visit the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?b=651097&amp;u=530666&amp;m=53232&amp;urllink=&amp;afftrack=\">Varga Store</a> headquarters. I first fell in love with their location in Santa Monica many years ago when walking along Main Street. Now I love their shop in my local mall (within walking distance), so when we discussed pulling clothes, I got pretty excited. As a former stylist, the best part about putting an outfit together is the opportunity to get creative with mixing and matching items. I really enjoy putting a twist on pieces that you may not think go together - like <a href=\"http://shrsl.com/?~72z4\">this elephant top</a> - and ice cream necklace.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327625715-DC17HB10WID1RLW7042A/14b-IMG_1636.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The office was fashionable and functional and full of glamorous details.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327643289-32H2YYGQ2IA1XUS4ROX1/14c-IMG_1661.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327658872-VJ9XJYKU15MQ5PCHZMOS/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327673633-Z0TV3Z9H15ABK9GK22MD/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I posted this on <a href=\"http://instagram.com/amytangerine\">Instagram</a>, asking whether I should choose the citrus or pineapple dress...</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598327718319-9I1NLTNIXI409NJUHJE0/14f-IMG_1665.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Don't worry - I ended up getting both! If you have the chance to visit one of <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=599829&amp;m=53232&amp;afftrack=locations&amp;urllink=www%2Evargastore%2Ecom%2Fpages%2Flocations\">Varga's locations</a>, I highly recommend it. PS - <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?b=651097&amp;u=530666&amp;m=53232&amp;urllink=&amp;afftrack=\">Varga</a> is offering 30% off their entire site this weekend! At checkout, use promo code: ladyblue</p><p>Thinking about adding a Fashion Friday post here on the blog every once in a while. Hope you're into it!</p><p>Photos by <a href=\"http://jacshoot.com/blog\">Jamie Waters</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}